							</div>
							<p class="nomargin"><span class="color_red">佘大湿</span>回复说：期待实景图~~</p>
						</div>
						<div class="review_item">
							<p class="review_name"><span class="pull-right">2013-04-28</span><strong>Jane</strong></p>
							<div class="clearfix">
								<span class="review_btns pull-right">
									<a href="javascript:;"><i class="i_icon i_icon_big i_icon_review"></i>回复</a>
									<a href="javascript:;"><i class="i_icon i_icon_big i_icon_del"></i>删除</a>
								</span>
								<p class="review_txt border_dot_b1">很好！非常好用的工具！</p>
							</div>
							<p class="nomargin"><span class="color_red">佘大湿</span>回复说：期待实景图~~</p>
						</div>
						<div class="review_item">
							<p class="review_name"><span class="pull-right">2013-04-28</span><strong>Jane</strong></p>
							<div class="clearfix">
								<span class="review_btns pull-right">
									<a href="javascript:;"><i class="i_icon i_icon_big i_icon_review"></i>回复</a>
									<a href="javascript:;"><i class="i_icon i_icon_big i_icon_del"></i>删除</a>
								</span>
								<p class="review_txt">很好！非常好用的工具！</p>
							</div>
							<form>
								<textarea class="textarea_def"></textarea>
								<div class="btn_group clearfix">
									<button type="submit" class="pull-left vote_btn vote_btn_small  noborder">提交留言</button>
									<a class="pull-left vote_btn vote_btn_small vote_btn_gray noborder">取消</a>
								</div>
							</form>
						</div>
						<div class="review_item">
							<p class="review_name"><span class="pull-right">2013-04-28</span><strong>Jane</strong></p>
							<div class="clearfix">
								<span class="review_btns pull-right">
									<a href="javascript:;"><i class="i_icon i_icon_big i_icon_review"></i>回复</a>
									<a href="javascript:;"><i class="i_icon i_icon_big i_icon_del"></i>删除</a>
								</span>
								<p class="review_txt border_dot_b1">很好！非常好用的工具！赞一个⋯⋯很好！</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

